OL,3,CBeamish named Art Fund's 'Museum of
OL,4,Cthe Year'
OL,6,FThe County Durham attraction Beamish
OL,7,Fhas been named the Art Fund's 'Museum
OL,8,Fof the Year' for 2025.
OL,10,FThe 'living museum of the North' beat
OL,11,Foff competition from four other
OL,12,Ffinalists at a ceremony in Liverpool
OL,13,Fon Thursday evening (26 June).
OL,15,FThe Museum will receive #120,000 in
OL,16,Fwhat is the biggest single arts prize
OL,17,Fin Britain and the largest museum
OL,18,Faward in the world.
