OL,3,CBeamish named Art Fund's 'Museum of
OL,4,Cthe Year'
OL,6,FRhiannon Hyles, chief executive of
OL,7,FBeamish, said the team are "incredibly
OL,8,Fexcited and truly elated."
OL,10,FShe added, "To receive such a
OL,11,Fprestigious award is a real honour, a
OL,12,Fphenomenal achievement, and is credit
OL,13,Fto the amazing people who make Beamish
OL,14,Fsuch a special place. Thank you to our
OL,15,Ffantastic staff and volunteers and our
OL,16,Fcommunities, visitors, supporters and
OL,17,Fpartners for their support."
