OL,3,CBeamish named Art Fund's 'Museum of
OL,4,Cthe Year'
OL,6,FThe other shortlisted museums, all
OL,7,Fhighly commended by the judges, were:
OL,8,FChapter (Cardiff), Compton Verney
OL,9,F(Warwickshire), Golden Thread Gallery
OL,10,F(Belfast) and Perth Museum (Perth &
OL,11,FKinross).
OL,13,FRecent figures from Visit Britain
OL,14,Fconfirmed that Beamish continues to
OL,15,Fmaintain its position as the most
OL,16,Fvisited paid attraction in the North
OL,17,FEast, with over 838,000 visitors last
OL,18,Fyear, a 5% increase on 2023.
