OL,6,FJenny Waldman, director of Art Fund
OL,7,Fand chair of the judging panel,
OL,8,Fdescribed Beamish as a "joyous,
OL,9,Fimmersive and unique place."
OL,11,FShe said, "The judges were blown away
OL,12,Fby the remarkable attention to detail
OL,13,Fof its exhibits across a 350 acre site
OL,14,Fand by the passion of its staff and
OL,15,Fvolunteers."
